By the time we get there,

840
00:41:36,340 --> 00:41:37,300
it'll be daylight.

841
00:41:38,780 --> 00:41:39,580
Then get some sleep.

842
00:41:40,488 --> 00:41:41,888
I'd better keep you company.

843
00:41:41,900 --> 00:41:44,111
Otherwise, we'll both be in trouble
if you fall asleep.

844
00:41:44,820 --> 00:41:46,260
As if that would happen.

845
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:47,500
No way.

846
00:41:52,220 --> 00:41:53,740
It's so dark outside.

847
00:41:54,222 --> 00:41:56,333
You can't even see
your hand in front of your face.

848
00:42:00,300 --> 00:42:00,820
Landlady.

849
00:42:03,780 --> 00:42:05,020
Are you afraid of ghosts?

850
00:42:06,780 --> 00:42:08,100
Of course not.

851
00:42:08,180 --> 00:42:08,700
Well...

852
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:10,580
Ghosts don't exist.

853
00:42:12,980 --> 00:42:14,780
But I've often heard that

854
00:42:16,100 --> 00:42:17,300
when you're driving at night,

855
00:42:17,860 --> 00:42:19,140
especially in a place like this,

856
00:42:20,380 --> 00:42:22,100
you'll sometimes see

857
00:42:22,100 --> 00:42:24,020
someone in white
trying to flag you down.

858
00:42:24,980 --> 00:42:25,820
And then,

859
00:42:26,180 --> 00:42:28,340
if the driver kindly lets them in,

860
00:42:29,300 --> 00:42:30,180
guess what happens

861
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:31,100
before long?

862
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:32,780
It gets colder

863
00:42:34,220 --> 00:42:35,300
and colder

864
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:37,220
inside the car.

865
00:42:39,820 --> 00:42:41,740
Sometimes a cold breeze
even blows through.

866
00:42:43,022 --> 00:42:45,888
The temperature inside the car
suddenly drops by more than ten degrees.

867
00:42:45,977 --> 00:42:46,555
You know?

868
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:49,180
Slowly, the windows

869
00:42:49,860 --> 00:42:51,020
start to fog up.

870
00:42:51,820 --> 00:42:53,580
And your vision
gets blurrier and blurrier.

871
00:42:57,580 --> 00:42:58,180
Look.

872
00:42:58,660 --> 00:42:59,940
Isn't that someone wearing white?

873
00:43:00,180 --> 00:43:01,620
I don't know about outside,

874
00:43:01,733 --> 00:43:04,244
but there's definitely
someone wearing white in this car.

875
00:43:05,020 --> 00:43:06,860
=Love Has Fireworks=
(Next Episode Preview)

876
00:43:07,100 --> 00:43:08,740
Hello, Yu? You called me?

877
00:43:08,740 --> 00:43:09,380
I just woke up.

878
00:43:09,940 --> 00:43:11,740
Gosh, you were sleeping?

879
00:43:12,020 --> 00:43:13,660
HR couldn't reach you,

880
00:43:13,660 --> 00:43:14,460
so they called me.

881
00:43:16,060 --> 00:43:17,700
You went to Chengdu recently?

882
00:43:18,020 --> 00:43:19,820
You sure know a lot
about my whereabouts.

883
00:43:20,460 --> 00:43:20,980
How was it?

884
00:43:21,900 --> 00:43:22,660
The Chengdu trip.

885
00:43:23,660 --> 00:43:25,340
Haven't you received

886
00:43:26,780 --> 00:43:27,980
the investigation report?

887
00:43:30,200 --> 00:43:31,288
Hello, Mr. Jiang?

888
00:43:32,820 --> 00:43:33,300
What?

889
00:43:44,711 --> 00:43:49,071
♪There's no need
to know the ending from the start♪

890
00:43:51,411 --> 00:43:56,541
♪Let the melody play through the chords
with the wind♪

891
00:43:59,651 --> 00:44:03,861
♪There's no need
to keep every promise from the past♪

892
00:44:06,191 --> 00:44:12,181
♪Leave some surprises
for the unknown in life♪

893
00:44:14,321 --> 00:44:19,311
♪There's no need
to force things between two people♪

894
00:44:20,981 --> 00:44:26,801
♪Perhaps I'll feel alone,
yet still find you there for me♪

895
00:44:29,041 --> 00:44:34,751
♪There's no need
to dwell on right or wrong, nor fear♪

896
00:44:35,681 --> 00:44:42,311
♪A hug means more
than countless apologies♪

897
00:44:42,531 --> 00:44:45,661
♪I'll send you into the wide world♪

898
00:44:45,931 --> 00:44:49,811
♪To live with passion
and become who you truly are♪

899
00:44:50,481 --> 00:44:52,211
♪A quiet shoulder♪

900
00:44:52,211 --> 00:44:57,081
♪Like a harbor waiting
for your wandering soul♪

901
00:44:57,471 --> 00:45:00,451
♪I'll wait for the day
you return to a simpler life♪

902
00:45:00,681 --> 00:45:04,801
♪The lights of home warm the night♪

903
00:45:05,201 --> 00:45:07,291
♪A companionship that lasts forever♪

904
